'''2010年里約熱內盧洪水和泥石流災害'''是一場在2010年1月發生於[[巴西|巴西]][[里約熱內盧州|里約熱內盧州]]的[[極端氣候|極端氣候]]事件，已造成至少85人罹難<ref name="ABC1">{{cite news|url=http://www.abc.net.au/news/stories/2010/01/03/2784418.htm?section=world|title=More deaths feared after Brazil landslides|last=News|first=ABC|date=January 3, 2010|publisher=ABC News|accessdate=10 January 2010}}</ref>, 包含[[山崩|山崩]]壓垮桑基酒店建築物（Hotel Sankey）中的29人<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.abc.net.au/news/stories/2010/01/02/2784159.htm|title=29 dead as mudslide wipes out hotel|last=News|first=ABC|date=January 2, 2010|publisher=ABC News|accessdate=10 January 2010|archive-date=2011-02-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110204052608/http://www.abc.net.au/news/stories/2010/01/02/2784159.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>, 逾4000人被迫撤離家園<ref name="BBC03">{{citation | title = Brazil landslides 'may close nuclear plants' | url = http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/americas/8438842.stm | publisher = BBC News | date = 3 January 2010 | accessdate = 2010-02-21 | archive-date = 2019-09-07 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190907121857/http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/americas/8438842.stm | dead-url = no }}.</ref>。

受影響最嚴重的地區是里約熱內盧西南方約150公里（95英里）的[[安格拉多斯黑斯|安格拉多斯黑斯]]城市。<ref name="Reuters">{{citation | title = Brazil death toll from floods, mudslides rises to 64 | url = http://www.reuters.com/article/idUSTRE6000RD20100102 | publisher = Reuters | date = 2 January 2010 | accessdate = 2010-02-21 | archive-date = 2010-03-06 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20100306004810/http://www.reuters.com/article/idUSTRE6000RD20100102 | dead-url = no }}.</ref>而巴西唯一運轉中的[[核電廠|核電廠]]，[[安格拉核電廠|安格拉核電廠]]也位於受災區域，已暫時關閉<ref name="BBC03"/>。

